General.Name: Teck Guan Perdana Bhd
General.Description: Teck Guan Perdana Berhad, an investment holding company, manufactures, processes, and sells cocoa butter and powder, and other cocoa products in Malaysia. The company operates through Cocoa Products and Oil Palm Products segments. It is also involved in trading and sale of dried cocoa beans and crude palm kernel oil; and operation of kernel crushing plant, and oil palm and cocoa plantations. The company was formerly known as Creative Balance Sdn Bhd and changed its name to Teck Guan Perdana Berhad in May 1995. The company was incorporated in 1994 and is headquartered in Tawau, Malaysia. Teck Guan Perdana Berhad is a subsidiary of HTG Holdings Sdn. Bhd.
